      <title>芝加哥市长在最新动荡中任命新学校董事会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chicago-mayor-appoints-a-new-school-board-in-latest-upheaval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊周一宣布了该市公立学校董事会的新成员名单。上周，约翰逊表示，由于预算短缺问题日益紧张，他之前任命的所有董事都将辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chicago-mayor-appoints-a-new-school-board-in-latest-upheaval</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:23:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊丽莎白·沃伦敦促可口可乐、百事可乐、通用磨坊应对缩减通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/warren-presses-coca-cola-pepsi-general-mills-on-shrinkflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可口可乐、百事可乐和通用磨坊正受到参议院民主党人伊丽莎白·沃伦和众议员玛德琳·迪恩的审查，他们指责这些公司利用紧缩性通胀来牟取消费者暴利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/warren-presses-coca-cola-pepsi-general-mills-on-shrinkflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就 F-35 达成的协议让洛克希德公司得以收回被扣留的款项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/us-deal-on-f-35s-allows-lockheed-to-win-back-withheld-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国项目经理称，五角大楼已与洛克希德·马丁公司就该公司可在年底前达到的里程碑达成一致，以获得因缺乏必要的硬件和软件升级而可能被扣留的 5 亿美元付款中的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/us-deal-on-f-35s-allows-lockheed-to-win-back-withheld-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
