    <item>
      <title>以色列称在战争一周年之际拦截了哈马斯火箭弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防军称，他们拦截了伊朗支持的哈马斯向特拉维夫发射的大部分火箭弹，经过一年的战争，双方的战斗于周一进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 15:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德斯雅尔丹警告称美国大选后加拿大经济将遭遇“特朗普衰退”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/desjardins-warns-of-trump-slump-for-canada-s-economy-after-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德斯雅尔丹银行的经济学家表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普赢得总统大选，且共和党控制众议院和参议院，到 2028 年底，加拿大实际国内生产总值可能比卡玛拉·哈里斯获胜时下降 1.7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/desjardins-warns-of-trump-slump-for-canada-s-economy-after-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 15:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙银行在暴利税审查后面临额外支付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/spanish-banks-face-extra-payments-after-windfall-tax-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[审查发现西班牙最大的几家银行少缴了暴利税，因此需要向政府支付额外款项，这可能会影响第三季度的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/spanish-banks-face-extra-payments-after-windfall-tax-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 15:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市“放射性”市长从狂妄自大变为麻木不仁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eric-adams-investigation-nyc-s-mayor-goes-from-swagger-to-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市长面临刑事指控，他的亲密盟友正在逃离政府，警察局的高层陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eric-adams-investigation-nyc-s-mayor-goes-from-swagger-to-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 14:29:40 GMT</pubDate>
